# Edge Detection using OpenCV

This project performs edge detection on an image using OpenCV.

## Features
- Converts image to grayscale
- Applies Gaussian Blur for preprocessing
- Performs Canny edge detection
- Displays original and processed images
- Custom text overlay added

## Technologies Used
- Python
- OpenCV

## Author
Ishaani Prashant

## How to Run

1. Install dependencies:
   pip install opencv-python

2. Run the program:
   python main.py
